step1: install mongodb driver from npm

installation:
    npm install mongodb

commands:

table-  collection

insert-insertOne,insertMany

record -document

select -findOne,find

order by-sort

delete=deleteOne,deleteMany

update-updateOne,updateMany


projection in mongodb:

  by using this we can decide what are all the columns we need form a collection

  eg:0 for first columns and 1 for second columns


  0-except that column
  1-only that column


sorting:

   ascending to descending means 1
   descending to ascending means -1




